GM to Build Plant to Make Chevrolet Cars in Turkey, Sabah Says

-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 
2011-03-02T07:56:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/gm-to-build-plant-to-make-chevrolet-cars-in-turkey-sabah-says.html
  General Motors Co . is in talks with
Turkish authorities to build a plant in western Kocaeli province
to make Chevrolet cars,  Sabah  reported, citing Kocaeli chamber
of industry head Ayhan Zeytinoglu.  The plant will be an assembly line, Zeytinoglu said,
according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net . 